messages.text: aurora gates? i have something for you
who is this?
i'm a friend of your birth parents
what do u mean, my birth parents?
you live with an adoptive family, don't you?
well, yeah, but NOBODY knows that...i'm not supposed to talk about it...who are you?
i worked with your parents. i was with them the night they died. i have some things from them I need to get to you.
OMG. i didn't realize. were you in the car crash too?
there wasn't a car crash, aurora
your parents were killed, and i'm afraid their killers might have figured out where we've hidden you.
WTF what do you mean? who would want to kill them?
they were targeted by russian spies...your parents worked for the CIA
no, they were telemarketers. who are u?
my code name for this operation is agent harris
there is a russian sleeper agent somewhere at your school aware of your real identity.
my mission is to help you get to safety
i don't believe this
don't you think it's strange you're not allowed to talk about your birth parents?
well yes but...that's just the way it is. i was only three when it happened
You need to leave school right now and head downtown to our safe house
right now? but 5th period is about to start! i can't skip school!
your life may depend on it
...aurora?
alright. give me a minute
ok i told ms. webster i needed to go to the nurse. but my bike is on the other side of campus...
you need to go downtown as soon as possible. I'll give you an address once you're close
omg i think principal johnson saw me from his office window. what do i do?
continue walking. act normal. don't be conspicuous
oh no, he's getting up from his chair. what do i do?
don't panic. just tell him you're going to the bathroom
alright. i told him that the girl's bathroom closer to my class room was out of order
he let me go, but as soon as the janitor goes to fix it, they'll know i ditched!
it's ok. you'll be gone by then
i've got my bike...i'm on my way
i'm almost downtown, where exactly is this safe house?
head to the pond at coleson park. your contact will meet you there to verify you haven't been intercepted
what do you mean? I thought I was going to a SAFE house, not an open park!
i have to make sure you aren't being held hostage or being impersonated by the sleeper agent at your school
alright...i'll let you know when i get there. i don't like this though. it's so obvious i'm a kid ditching school
agent pope says you are present and alone. that's good. go to the pond
where's agent pope? i don't see him. this is creepy
there's nobody down by the pond except a little old lady feeding the ducks
Wait
ok...
well, 5 minutes later i've had a very awkward conversation with an old lady about my life & “kids these days”
is she still there?
no, she left & gave me her bread to finish feeding the ducks
OMG THERE'S AN ADRESS BAKED INTO THIS SLICE OF BREAD
that's the safe house
THAT was agent pope?
ok. I'm going to head over to
OH NO
what's wrong, Aurora?
it's principal johnson! he's got police officers with him!
they're looking for me! i've got to run!
Don't draw attention to yourself!
damnit! they saw me sprinting away
if principal johnson is with them instead of at school...he may well be the russian agent
you'll have to lose them before you head to the safe house
i'm heading across the street to the mall. I think I can lose them in there
Keep me posted
Harris?
are you secure?
i made it to the mall. i'm hiding in a dressing room
you can't hide. they'll eventually find you. you need to get out of there
just act calm, right?
exactly
i bought a hoodie & am wearing it now
good thinking. it'll be harder for them to identify you
i don't have my bike anymore, but I think I can walk from here
you're close to the safe house. text me when you get there
am...am i here?
i can see you on the security cameras; you're definitely here.
you look a lot like your mother, too.
uhhh...thanks...
are you serious though? this bowling alley is a safe house?
go in and ask the clerk for shoes size ten and a half, extra wide
this place is so sad & rundown...
it's only a cover. did you ask agent garfield for the shoes?
i just did. he said he'd have to “take me back & check” if they had a pair
oh my gosh, there's a trap door back here
it's a fully furnished apartment down there. you should be comfortable while our other agents check out johnson
your original birth certificate, social security number, and legal documentation is down there too
there are racks & racks of bowling balls here...and filing cabinets?
yes. your whole family's file should be there
oh wow. spain, africa, hong kong, moscow...my parents traveled all over the world!
until...oh. they stopped when I was born...
they were fantastic spies, but you were their priority. i was sorry to see them leave the CIA to be full-time parents
russian intelligence was convinced they were still active, and hunted them down.
they think you're already doing work for us too
have you found your documents yet?
yeah, they're right here
my real name is penelope tanner? o_O
OH MY GOD
what's the matter!?
I HAVE AN INHERITENCE
oh yes. that. your parents wanted to make sure you were taken care of
it's $2M in a bank somewhere in switzerland!!!!!
once you resume your real identity as penelope tanner you'll have access to it
what do you mean?
you're not aurora gates, you're penelope tanner.
we can get you to switzerland and help you start your life, safe from foreign agents.
but...what about my family?
your adoptive parents?
yeah, my FAMILY.
omg, what was that noise upstairs? I think I heard gunshots o_O
agent garefield isn't responding.
we have footage of johnson from the security cameras.
oh my god! he's coming for me! he's going to kill me!
don't worry. agent pope and others are on their way already. Just stay hidden
but you said if I hide I'll eventually be found D:
not before the other agents arrive
i hear footsteps right above me. he's going to come down & find all the top secret files!
he's at the trap door! i can hear him trying to get it open!
stay calm. find some place to hide within the safe room and keep texting me
there's nowhere to hide!
i can't do this!
yes, you can!
aurora?
aurora, confirm your status
oh god
what have I done?
what? what did you do?
when he came down...there were all the bowling balls...I just chucked one at him.
it knocked him off his feet & then he hit his head on a filing cabinet
...is he still breathing?
yeah, but he's bleeding a lot. what did i just do to the principal...
he's not your principal, he's a russian spy working to kill you and find our division's CIA archives.
OMG I hear more people upstairs!
don't worry, that's agent pope and the others. i have them on screen. they'll be able to help
what's your status, aurora?
they're transporting him now. the little old lady...agent pope...is doing first aid. they say he's going to be OK
that was some quick thinking on your part. you've handled this all very impressively. your parents would be proud
...thanks, agent harris
how would you like to follow in their footsteps?
i can arrange to have you started in the CIA's field agent training academy
you would make a fantastic spy, penelope tanner.
thanks, but no.
oh really? why??
i just want to go home to my family. think everything over.
i'm not ready to be penelope tanner. I'm still just aurora, so I have to decline
at least, for now.
